sqlSchema.tableSchema:
CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE `default`.`admirals`(
  `id` int)
ROW FORMAT SERDE 
  'org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.lazy.LazySimpleSerDe' 
STORED AS INPUTFORMAT 
  'org.apache.hadoop.mapred.TextInputFormat' 
OUTPUTFORMAT 
  'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.HiveIgnoreKeyTextOutputFormat'
LOCATION
  'file:/opt/hive/data/warehouse/admirals'
TBLPROPERTIES (
  'TRANSLATED_TO_EXTERNAL'='TRUE', 
  'bucketing_version'='2', 
  'external.table.purge'='TRUE')

CREATE TABLE `default`.`depts`(
  `deptno` int, 
  `deptname` varchar(256), 
  `locationid` int)
ROW FORMAT SERDE 
  'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.orc.OrcSerde' 
STORED AS INPUTFORMAT 
  'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.orc.OrcInputFormat' 
OUTPUTFORMAT 
  'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.orc.OrcOutputFormat'
LOCATION
  'file:/opt/hive/data/warehouse/depts'
TBLPROPERTIES (
  'bucketing_version'='2', 
  'transactional'='true', 
  'transactional_properties'='default')

CREATE TABLE `default`.`emps`(
  `empid` int, 
  `deptno` int, 
  `name` varchar(256), 
  `salary` float, 
  `hire_date` timestamp)
ROW FORMAT SERDE 
  'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.orc.OrcSerde' 
STORED AS INPUTFORMAT 
  'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.orc.OrcInputFormat' 
OUTPUTFORMAT 
  'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.orc.OrcOutputFormat'
LOCATION
  'file:/opt/hive/data/warehouse/emps'
TBLPROPERTIES (
  'bucketing_version'='2', 
  'transactional'='true', 
  'transactional_properties'='default')

CREATE TABLE `default`.`mv1`(
  `empid` int, 
  `deptname` varchar(256), 
  `hire_date` timestamp)
ROW FORMAT SERDE 
  'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.orc.OrcSerde' 
STORED AS INPUTFORMAT 
  'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.orc.OrcInputFormat' 
OUTPUTFORMAT 
  'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.orc.OrcOutputFormat'
LOCATION
  'file:/opt/hive/data/warehouse/mv1'
TBLPROPERTIES (
  'bucketing_version'='2')

CREATE VIEW `default`.`ok_movies` AS select `u_data`.`userid`, `u_data`.`movieid`, `u_data`.`rating`, `u_data`.`unixtime` from `default`.`u_data`
where `u_data`.`rating` >= 2 and `u_data`.`rating` <=4

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE `default`.`u_data`(
  `userid` int, 
  `movieid` int, 
  `rating` int, 
  `unixtime` string)
ROW FORMAT SERDE 
  'org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.lazy.LazySimpleSerDe' 
WITH SERDEPROPERTIES ( 
  'field.delim'='\t', 
  'serialization.format'='\t') 
STORED AS INPUTFORMAT 
  'org.apache.hadoop.mapred.TextInputFormat' 
OUTPUTFORMAT 
  'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.HiveIgnoreKeyTextOutputFormat'
LOCATION
  'file:/opt/hive/data/warehouse/u_data'
TBLPROPERTIES (
  'TRANSLATED_TO_EXTERNAL'='TRUE', 
  'bucketing_version'='2', 
  'external.table.purge'='TRUE')

CREATE VIEW `default`.`ok_movies` AS select `u_data`.`userid`, `u_data`.`movieid`, `u_data`.`rating`, `u_data`.`unixtime` from `default`.`u_data`
where `u_data`.`rating` >= 2 and `u_data`.`rating` <=4
